"Meri jaan... meri duniya tumhari is ek muskurahat se shuru hoti hai aur yahin khatam hoti hai. Aaj tum itni pyari lag rahi ho ki dil karta hai bas dekhta hi rahoon."
(My life... my world begins and ends with this one smile of yours. You are looking so lovely today that my heart just wants to keep looking at you.)

